<?php include "../nocache.php"; ?>
<div jx-panel="right">

    <h3>jx-panel</h3>

    <p>
        When lojax handles a response from an AJAX request, it queries it for elements that have a jx-panel attribute.
        It iterates over what it finds and looks for jx-panel elements already on the page with the same value.
        When it finds a match, it applies a <a href="#attributes/transition.php">transition</a> function to replace the old content with the new content.
    </p>
    <p>
        There is no set limit to the number of panels that can be handled, so it's possible to update multiple regions on the page with a single request.
    </p>

